metadata.title: globalartdepot 16X20 inch Picasso Pablo Maya la PouPe 1938 Canvas Print RePro
features: Part Number: Z900554 Image Size: 16 X 20 inch or 41 X 51 cm. Canvas Size: 17X22 inch or 43X56 cm. Canvas Thickness: 18 mils.
This is an excellent print on canvas that lasts 100+ years under normal conditions. Not hand-painted, not cheap paper poster either, but it looks like a real oil painting!
Frame not Included. Professional stretching or framing is optional to order by the following instruction.
Order only optional stretching by searching "STRETCH1620" at Amazon.
Order optional stretching and framing by searching "BTSS1620", "MTSS1620", "P5000-100S1620", "M002BS1620", "P3059-177S1620" or "B003S1620" at Amazon.
description: The canvas is a fine woven blend of polyflax and cotton, and is specially coated with an acid free acrylic titanium gesso to provide long term archival quality. UltraChrome pigment inks with over 16 million colors make art works on such canvas perfect.
